|||locate the statue of the horse|||to its right is a lamp post|||waldo is on the bottom left of the lamp post
|||turn and face the wooden wagon.|||notice the tiles in front of the wagon.|||waldo is located two tiles above the first wheel on the left.
|||look for the lamp post next to the open door with a small green and white sign above it.|||look at the top left corner of that open doorway.|||waldo is at that corner, with his head touching it.

|||look at the wall with a barrel hanging over it.
|||focus on the display to the right of the barrel.
|||waldo is on the left edge of this display, about one waldo down from the top.

|||find the stairs behind the horse statue and turn so they're at your back.|||look at the skylight from this side.|||from the furthest part you'll see a straight bar, a horizontal one, straight, horizontal and above this one is another horizontal. waldo is above that in the sky, where that bar and the one to its right make a v.

|||turn until you're facing the doorway leading to a dark room closest to you, with a lamp post on the left side of it.|||look at the terracotta roof right above the doorway.|||waldo is on the roof, above the left side of the doorway, body in the shady part of the roof, to the right of the top left doorway corner, and hand to the right of the green sign above the doorway.
|||look at the horse statue|||to the right is a lamp post|||waldo is one third up the lamp post

|||find the lady with blue and white shirt colors, on the corner of the room .|||locate the air device on top to the right of her head.|||going in the same direction to the ceiling theres a another air device a big one find it.|||waldo is on top of the big light on the ceiling in between the air device and the light.
|||look for the man with the yellow shirt leaning on a green table.|||there is a fluorescent light straight above him.|||waldo is just to the right of the distant end of that light.
|||find the lady with a blue shirt|||on top of her theres a tv and a fan find them|||waldo is in the middle of the fan and the tv

|||find the lady in the yellow shirt,she has her hand on the table behind her|||to the left of the lady is a person sitting at a table and about to take a bite of food|||waldo is on the this persons chair,on the persons butt

|||find the person in a yellow shirt and tan shorts with boots standing at the service counter.|||above and to the left of the counter are some shelves with jars stacked on them.|||waldo is on the top right corner of these jars wit his body on the light that runs left and right.

|||note the woman and man dining right near you|||the woman has a backpack on the seat by her|||waldo is right on the right edge of the back pack near the top where the zipper would run and also on the right side of her red shorts leg
|||look for the balding man in a white and blue shirt who is sitting at a table by himself|||look to his left side|||waldo is on that side just above his belt
|||look for the older man and the woman talking|||look at the woman's back|||waldo is on the woman's middle back a little to the left

|||find the service counter that has the guy in khaki short, and yellow shirt at it.|||to the left a bit, you'll see a silver case of sorts on the end of this service counter, to the lower right of the three shelves packed with containers.|||waldo is sitting on top of the top left corner of the glass on this case, so that his head is brushing the fluorescent above him.

|||find the man sitting alone at a table wearing a blue and white striped shirt.|||look at the empty chair diagonal from his position.|||notice the metal ring under the seat.|||waldo is on the part of the metal ring that is facing you with his head grazing the seat.

|||find the woman in a blue shirt sitting at a table by herself in the corner under a tv.|||look at the rectangular ceiling light above her.|||waldo is sitting on this light directly in the middle such that his body is on the light and his head is on the ceiling.
|||turn towards the table where a woman and a man with a white shirt is located.|||turn and center the frame on the man.|||waldo is on the right side of his chest.
|||locate the table that is in the middle of a white column|||find a green book on that table|||waldo is on top of the green book

|||find the table where several diners are eating and there is a satchel on the floor next to the moan wearing a grey blazer.|||turn to the table on the right that is empty and has a green menu, 2 ashtrays, a coffee cup and a white pillar in the middle of the table.

|||look at the top of the white pillar where it meats the green ceiling and waldo is directly on top of the white pillar to the right on the green ceiling
|||look at the tree closest to you with the hats hanging on it|||look at the brown hat on the right side of the tree|||look a few inches to the right of that hat and waldo is in the white square

|||look on the floor for a circular design that looks like a rug|||near there is a green section of a wall that leads to a kitchen|||on the green part of the wall, on the left, on the floor, where the white meets the green is waldo

|||look for the people standing near the counter.|||focus on the guy on the right with his right arm appearing to be scooping or grabbing something.|||see where the hanging light over his head attaches to the ceiling.|||waldo is just to the top left of where this light attaches to the ceiling.

|||right near you is a dried up tree with hats hung on it.|||halfway up there is a straw hat, the lowest hat.|||waldo is on the trunk of the tree, his head very slightly below the highest point of the hat.

|||watch out for snakes and find the blue one on the ground slithering towards you.|||follow the length of the snake to a man entering a doorway.|||waldo is hiding just above the center of this doorway.

|||look toward the serving area where there is a group of four standing men.|||regarding the man on the far right, there is a light hanging from the ceiling above him.|||waldo is above this light slightly left of center with his head barely touching where the wall meets the ceiling.
|||find the empty circular table that has a column through it.|||look for a painting on the column.|||waldo's left shoulder is in the very top left of the painting.

|||look down at the middle circle center of the floor, where it is wood and not brick.|||you'll see a table that has two double chairs and two regular chairs.|||look between the single chair and double chair closest to the center of the circle.|||waldo is on the floor between the shadows those two chairs make. if you think of it as a triangle, waldo is in the middle of the fattest part of the triangle between the shadows.
|||face the square windows.|||turn left until you see a round pillar.|||waldo is to the left and middle of the pillar.
|||locate the big window|||there will be two brown pillars on either side of the window|||waldo's head will be touching the bottom right corner of the pillar on the right

|||find the two round table with red tops.|||look to the left edge of the right table.|||follow it up to a triple dotted light behind slats of wood that almost look like a fence.|||waldo is on the fence to the right of this light.

|||at the center of the room look at the white table with no chairs next to it, right on the edge of the wooden floor and the bricks
|||to the right of this is a large golden pillar with a chair directly in front of its base
|||waldo is on the pillar about halfway up

|||as you look around the room you will notice there are 4 large round brown pillars|||find the window and focus on the pillar to the right of the window|||waldo is a quarter of the way down from the top of the pillar

|||locate the circular, red tables near you.|||look at the circular red table on your left.|||focus on the round pillar behind this table.|||waldo is three quarters of the way up this pillar on the right side.

|||find the table with a white table cloth and a vase of sticks on it.|||look one table to the right.|||focus on the chair nearest to you.|||waldo is on the floor next to the front left leg such that the leg is in the gap between his head and arm.
|||find the ceiling fan|||look to the left, by the dinner poster|||waldo is on the wall against the ceiling between the dinner poster and the air vent to the left of it
|||look for the table with two people sitting across from each other.|||find the table against the wall and directly behind the person in the blue shirt.|||waldo is on the chair closest to you.
|||find the prague post newspaper handing on the wall that says "star struck"|||turn around 180 degrees|||waldo is sitting on top of the paper that looks like it is falling off the wall towards you.

|||scan the walls around you until a large grey elephant head jumps out at you.|||look at the bright sun lit window to the left of this elephant.|||you'll find waldo hiding underneath the bench underneath the center of that window.
|||look for the single table near the window|||to the right of the table you will see newspapers hanging on the wall|||on the middle edge of the second newspaper is where you'll find waldo

|||find the traffic light on the wall by a post with newspapers.|||look to the right of this post and down to see a rectangular table.|||a little further to the right you will see a round table.|||waldo is on the ground between these tables. he is to the right of the right further corner of the rectangle table and about a third of the way across the floor to the round table.

|||turn to face the wall closest to you with newspapers hanging from it
|||note the traffic light hanging from the left edge of this wall
|||note that the traffic light looks to be cut into four sections on its side, waldo is on the second section counting from the top, near where that white line is on the left

|||look down to the sort of painting or mirror on the wall which falls under the visible arch before that wall|||note that there's a light or object on the center of the arch|||waldo is just to the right of the little ornament on the wall, also intersecting the mirror

|||locate the blueish newspapers hanging near you.
|||focus on the one with rocks on it, it's a pile of something at least.
|||waldo is to the immediate left of the top point of the rocks.

|||turn to face a tv above the red carpet strip.|||to your left is a small table with a plant between you and it.|||there's two red napkins. go to the left one.|||on the right tip of that napkin is waldo.

|||look for the tv hanging above the doorway.|||go up to the trim on the outside part of the ceiling, below the yellow and red patterned wall.|||to the right of the right light, on the yellow strip between the two pieces of trim, waldo is hiding.
|||turn and face the wall where there are red and black checkers.|||on the opposite site you should see a tv mounted on the wall.|||waldo is on the top left of the tv.
|||turn to face the kitchen|||there will be a table on the left side of your vision|||find the left most table leg for that table|||waldo is one waldo length to the left of that leg
|||look towards the bar where all the people are sitting|||turn right 90 degrees.|||you will see two people sitting at a table|||on the ceiling, slightly to the left of the table, waldo is hiding

|||turn so that there is an empty square table with a red runner in front of you.|||directly behind that is another empty square table that looks the same, with a small round red thing on top of the runner.|||waldo is on the wall behind the far table, if you follow the little red ball straight up about half an inch.

|||find the table with 4 people in it|||behind them theres another table with 2 people in it locate that|||behind the 2 people theres an empty table find it|||waldo is on top of the table right in the middle of the table

|||there is an empty round table with a red centerpiece very close to you|||just beyond and to the left of the table is a door that looks like goes under stairs|||waldo is to the top right of the door and his hat is directly under the triangle from the beam

|||face the rectangular table with a red table runner and a column at the left side.|||look at the left corner of the table closest to you.|||waldo is sitting just slightly to the left of this corner, and the bottom right of his torso is touching the corner.

|||notice the 4 people sitting at the table with a blonde girl on the right|||to the left of her is a short haired guy in a black sweater|||waldo is on his right shoulder toward the black haired girl with his hand between that guy's eyes

|||look for the close door under the stairs.|||look at the top left corner of that door.|||waldo is in the black area above the top left corner of the door. you can see a little black below him so just give him a little room above the bottom of the black.

|||look for the lighted corner of the bar.
|||on the left side, are four bar stools.
|||look between the two bar stools on the right side.
|||there is a foot rest near the bottom of the stools. waldo is in between these stools right with the foot rest area.

|||look to the corner of the room that has a very visible glare from a light source
|||examine the ceiling close to the light source - notice there is a large metal panel rectangle from the ceiling. there are multiple rectangles on the ceiling but focus on the one closest to that light source
|||notice that the rectangle is divided into four long columns
|||waldo is between the first and second column from the left, right in the middle
|||face the table with a red runner and small red object as the centerpiece.|||find the front right side of the back left chair, not the ones near the camera.|||waldo is on the top right side.

|||find the group of people sitting around a table.|||center the camera around the person with a blurry head and light sweater.|||rotate the camera upward until you can also see the orange part of the ceiling.|||waldo is directly above the person's head on the orange part of the ceiling.

|||there is a table with people sitting at.
|||the left side of the table, sits a man. there is also an arched pathway that runs above.
|||waldo is on the arch way, towards the top above the mans head. also, his location is a bit right of the center width wise. this may be considered about 40 percent of the way completely around the archway, front to back.

|||look for the table with four men sitting at it.|||to the left of that table is a wall with two pictures.|||go up from between the two pictures to the ceiling.|||waldo is on the ceiling with his head just below the bright light on the ceiling.

|||locate the middle window.
